name: django
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "1.11.3" %}

package:
  name: django
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: django-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/D/Django/Django-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 9ef9de0a957245ed3a29c4162ed2fd493252ca249a755f9e2b4a9be82caf8f6b
  patches:
    # Hard-code gdal and geos' paths to the corresponding conda packages.
    - libgdal.patch
    - libgeos.patch

build:
  number: 0
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record=record.txt
  entry_points:
    - django-admin = django.core.management:execute_from_command_line

requirements:
  build:
    - python
    - setuptools
  run:
    - python
    - pytz
